title: Login Success
postconditions: Redirect to "Make Appointment" page
steps_actions:
1. Access page
2. Click Button "Make Appointment"
3. Input Username
4. Input Password
5. Click Button Login
steps_result:
1. Show CURA Healthcare Service page
2. Redirect to login page
3. Username is appear
4. Password is appear
5. Successfully loged in, redirect to "make appointment" page.

title: Make Appointment, Facility: Tokyo
postconditions: Successbook appointment and Showing Appointment Confirmation
steps_actions:
1. Access page
2. Select dropdown menu "Facility"
3. check the checkbox "Apply for hospital readmission"
4. Choose Radiobutton "Healthcare program"
5. Select visit date
6. Write a comment
7. Click button "Book Appointment"
steps_result:
1. Show appointment page
2. the selected dropdown appears
3. checklist appears
4. Clicked appears
5. visit date appears
6. Comments appears
7. Redirect to appointment confirmation page

3. checked
4. Medicare clicked
5. visit date selected
6. Write a comment
7.
